    analytic data sink.. Demonstration only. Typically you have to decide: log it and/or send it here instead? following to environment properties have to be set with keys from key.io website, to get data into keen.io:
    • env.getProperty("KEEN_PROJECT_ID")
    • env.getProperty("KEEN_WRITE_KEY")

    2015-03-28
